{"title":"迎春曲——街头诗一束（上）","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":2,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎春曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——街头诗一束（上）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给南水泉乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山是万宝山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树是摇钱树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手脑两勤快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝贝就出土。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙王"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何愁不下雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙王在人间——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山边挖大渠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村边造水站。　（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问龙王他是谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业社的社员！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）在怀来县南水泉乡和官厅水库的附近地区即将造一座电力扬水站。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再造一座长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红花搭成城楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿叶编成墙垛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再造一座万里长城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拦住飞沙走石。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让苇子和果树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长在官厅湖畔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝瓶和宝剑（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泉水好像一只宝瓶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手臂好像一把宝剑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把宝瓶背在肩上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向保守思想决一战；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再高高地举起宝剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把涝洼地变成稻田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）英雄董存瑞，幼年时候曾希望找到一只宝瓶，把泉水带到他的村子：怀来南山堡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树和种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一粒种子撒下土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵树苗就能长出。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丢掉了一粒种子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是丢掉一棵树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锄头和稻叉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锄头上看年景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——庄稼话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锄头上会滴水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻叉上会挂火；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锄头和稻叉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时刻不离手头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住在深山野谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播下你的种子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也能够收获，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几担谷子和水果。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和荒地打一仗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山谷隆隆地震动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩石摇摇地发抖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是英雄的锄头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在和荒地决斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒山终于卷起旗帜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯下腰来低下头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给山区"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山区如同一座宝库，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金的门槛银的窗户；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年二十四个节季，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个节季都有“秋”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山区到处都有得收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就看我们伸不伸手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拟动员令（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山是一面铜鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲吧，祖国在欢呼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锄头在空中一响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活就前进一步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拟动员令（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树木是旗，大地是鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄弟们，快挥起锄头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞砂走石；冰雪激流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经为春天让开一条路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于一寸土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕是一寸土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得到辛勤的栽培，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会有几担果子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和亩产千斤的谷穗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算一算这一笔账吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产潜力能有几倍？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个号召"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城虽说很古老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们倒是很年轻；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓起革命干劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过万里长城——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“遍山栽起摇钱树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水库变成聚宝盆！”　（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）这是怀来县委在千人大会上的一个号召"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决心书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手臂好比是长剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决心好比是火焰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在党的前面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写下一封决心书："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要用雪亮的长剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使地球摇摇发颤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一个春天里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栽起千亩果园！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}